ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/30381/', '', 'Amisulpride, Droperidol, Pimavanserin', 'Pentosan polysulfate, Calcium chloride, Phenazopyridine, Alprostadil, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Avanafil, Phenyl salicylate, Tadalafil, Magnesium hydroxide, Ammonium chloride, Dimethyl sulfoxide', 1767369485);
